{% block content %}
    <p>We will send a letter to your household asking the householder to answer questions about the property and the individuals living there.</p>
    <p>The householder is responsible for completing the census.</p>
    {% from "components/details/_macro.njk" import onsDetails %}
    {{
        onsDetails({
            "id": "details",
            "title": "What is a household and who is the householder?",
            "classes": "u-mb-m",
            "content": "<p>A <strong>household</strong> is either:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>one person living alone</li>
                            <li>a group of people (who don't have to be related) living at the same address who share cooking facilities and share a living or dining area</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>The <strong>householder</strong> is a person who individually or jointly meets at least one of following:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>owns or rents the property</li>
                            <li>is responsible for paying the household bills and expenses</li>
                        </ul>",
